-- Factbox: Forbes list of top 10 wealthiest Americans
-- 
-- Wed Sep 22, 2010 7:23pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/09/22/us-forbes400-fb-idUSTRE68L66X20100922

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - Forbes released its annual list on Wednesday of the 400 wealthiest Americans. 

 Following is the top 10 on the list: 1. Bill Gates, Microsoft $54 billion 2. Warren Buffett, Berkshire Hathaway $45 billion 3. Larry Ellison, Oracle Corp, $27 billion 4. Christy Walton and family, Wal-Mart $24 billion 5. Charles Koch, Koch Industries, $21.5 billion 6. David Koch, Koch Industries, $21.5 billion 7. Jim Walton, Wal-Mart, $20.1 billion 8. Alice Walton, Wal-Mart, $20 billion 9. S. Robson Walton, $19.7 billion 10. Michael Bloomberg, Bloomberg LP, $18 billion (Writing by  Ellen Wulfhorst ; editing by  Eric Walsh  and  Mohammad Zargham )